                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/14636.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Governor of Texas</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Austin</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-03-19">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 19, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Answering your telegram 18th instant concerning transportation of wounded
                    soldiers over Texas soil to Matamoros from Nueva Laredo, beg to advise it will
                    be agreeable to State of Texas to extend this permission.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Jas. E. Ferguson</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
